==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spreader
<hw>Spread"er</hw> <pr>(-⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>One who, or that which, spreads, expands, or propagates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A machine for combining and drawing fibers of flax
to form a sliver preparatory to spinning.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Spreadingly</ent>⟦br⟧
